summary: "It was very important to us that every frame of the movie was refined by the artists hand after the visuals were rendered by...
caption:
“It was very important to us that every frame of the movie was refined by the artists hand after the visuals were rendered by computers. If you freeze any part of the movie at any time, it will look like an illustration with hand drawn touches and all.”

Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse (2018), dir. Phil Lord & Christopher Miller

reblog.comment:
“It was very important to us that every frame of the movie was refined by the artists hand after the visuals were rendered by computers. If you freeze any part of the movie at any time, it will look like an illustration with hand drawn touches and all.”

Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse (2018), dir. Phil Lord & Christopher Miller

trail.content_raw:

Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse (2018), dir. Phil Lord & Christopher Miller
